Version 1.0 — 2026

Copyright (c) 2026 Elixpo (Ayushman Bhattacharya / @Circuit-Overtime)

This is a permissive, plain-English licence built on top of MIT. It is
written this way because we want the Oreo Badge to be picked up,
remixed, taught with, soldered, and gifted by as many curious people
as possible — and we want them to read the licence rather than skip it.

