TL;DR  (not legally binding; see the full grant below)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

  ✅ Use it.        Personally, in classrooms, at conferences, in
                    clubs, in lab work, on stage, on YouTube.
  ✅ Modify it.     Fork, hack, slice, rewrite. Ship new apps.
  ✅ Distribute it. Hand badges to friends. Sell kits. Run workshops.
  ✅ Commercial.    Yes — including selling badges with this OS on them.
  ⚠️  Credit us.    Keep our names + a link to the project visible in
                    your docs or about screen. Don't pretend you wrote it.
  ⚠️  Stay nice.    Follow the Code of Conduct when contributing back.
  ❌ No warranty.   It's a hobby project. If it sets your desk on fire,
                    that's between you and your desk.

